{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/JGitFlow/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Technical Debt"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"dfee596d-feb6-55b9-88ec-84bce5c0b4de","excerpt":"Le plugin maven jgit-flow est utilisé afin de simplifier au maximum la création d’une ”release” pour un module autonome : release-start : création d’une branche…","html":"<p>Le plugin maven <tt>jgit-flow</tt> est utilisé afin de simplifier au maximum la création d’une ”release” pour un module autonome :</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><tt>release-start</tt> :</p>\n<ul>\n<li>création d’une branche de stabilisation (”release”) pour une version donnée</li>\n<li>montée en version mineure de la branche <tt>develop</tt> ;</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><tt>release-finish</tt> : finalisation de la ”release” :</p>\n<ul>\n<li>suppression du suffix <tt>-SNAPSHOT</tt>,</li>\n<li>merge sur <tt>master</tt></li>\n<li>création du tag</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h1>Prérequis</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Vérifier que le pom.xml contient la configuration suivante :</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"xml\"><pre class=\"language-xml\"><code class=\"language-xml\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>plugin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>groupId</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>external.atlassian.jgitflow<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>groupId</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>artifactId</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>jgitflow-maven-plugin<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>artifactId</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>version</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>1.0-m5.1<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>version</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>configuration</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>flowInitContext</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n            <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>masterBranchName</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>master<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>masterBranchName</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n            <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>developBranchName</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>develop<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>developBranchName</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n            <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>versionTagPrefix</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>v-<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>versionTagPrefix</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>flowInitContext</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>noDeploy</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>true<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>noDeploy</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>squash</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>false<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>squash</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>scmCommentPrefix</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>[RELEASE] <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>scmCommentPrefix</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>useReleaseProfile</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>false<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>useReleaseProfile</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>configuration</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>plugin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>Avoir les branches locales <tt>develop</tt> et <tt>master</tt> à jour.</li>\n</ul>\n<h1>Démarrage de la ”release”</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\"> mvn jgitflow:release-start</code></pre></div>\n<h1>Finalisation de la ”release”</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\"> mvn jgitflow:release-finish</code></pre></div>\n<p>Puis, pousser les branches <tt>master</tt> et <tt>develop</tt> et les tags</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\"> git push origin master\n git push origin develop\n git push --tags</code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"JGitFlow","date":"May 12, 2017","description":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/JGitFlow/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/dynamicLogger/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Création dynamique d'un logger"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/shedlock/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"ShedLock"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383","916993862"]}